WEBVTT

00:00:57.123 --> 00:01:01.358
He was disgusted when talking to me,
as if he was saying to himself,

00:01:01.458 --> 00:01:05.400
"If this was the last girl on Earth,
I wouldn't look at her!"

00:01:05.450 --> 00:01:07.507
What's the meaning
of saying "menu" in Arabic?

00:01:07.578 --> 00:01:15.583
Two words made a Lebanese young man
judge a girl as being backward

00:01:16.323 --> 00:01:18.350
and ignorant.

00:01:18.820 --> 00:01:23.996
How could she speak that way?

00:01:24.346 --> 00:01:27.031
At that moment, I started thinking.

00:01:27.059 --> 00:01:28.107
It made me mad.

00:01:28.152 --> 00:01:29.236
It definitely hurts!

00:01:29.326 --> 00:01:32.391
I'm denied the right to speak
my own language in my own country?